## Summary
The SCIM API provides programmatic user and group provisioning for Amplitude organizations, implementing the SCIM 2.0 standard to enable integration with Identity Providers like Okta and JumpCloud, with endpoints for creating, reading, updating, and deleting users and permission groups.

